description: A Chef driven, local food experience, focusing on the delicate yet delicious element of smoke.  Our cuisine is creative, fun, and seasonal.   We cater to all occasions!  Chefs Joe Wolfson and Roland Feldman have spent many years in some of the countries top restaurants, and are ready to apply their love for food to your next special event or occasion.  We custom design menus based on our clients desires, to take an event from memorable to EPIC!
name: Smoke
